target: What area would you prefer it to be in?
context: <user>  I need information for a train from cambridge to norwich. <system>  There are several trains departing from Cambridge arriving in Norwich at a price of 17.60 pounds. What day are you looking to travel? <user>  I am looking to travel on Sunday, and leave after 21:30 <system>  I have train TR7767 leaving at 21:36 and arriving by 22:55. Would that be something that would work for you? <user>  Yes please book for 1 person and send the reference number. <system>  Okay, I've done that for you. Your reference number is 0TDRHZKN . <user>  Thank you. I also need a place to stay. Can you find me a three star guesthouse? <system>  Sure, what area of town are you interested in?<user>  In the centre I guess. I do need free parking. <system>  I'm sorry, there aren't any 3 star guesthouses in the centre, would you like to try another level?<user>  No, can you check for a 3 star guesthouse in the west? <system>  Yes, there is the hobsons house. Shall I go ahead and book that for you?<user>  Yes please. It will be for the same group of people for 3 nights starting on thursday. <system>  Okay, your booking was successful. Your reference number is 9CNY4IOQ .<user>  Thank you. Are there any colleges with free admission in the area? Or any other attractions that I may visit inbetween my meetings? <system>
